{"tid":1460543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(機場員工分析)對於機場怕困獸鬥，可以咁玩","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:38.000Z","uid":57044,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73fd471797be6e90598ea04d2c98c02641f103e7","tid":1460543,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"首先，大家811 退得咁快好大原因係機場本身個地形不利我地，成個赤立角係困獸鬥。所以我地如果唔想打困籠，可以選擇第二戰場，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">青衣</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPGPTaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPGPTaQ.png&h=a5ce73be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qx5w6xB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqx5w6xB.png&h=a109115a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅色係路障，藍色係前進路線，基本上我地係青衣方向集結，封住青馬大橋主要路口就已經成功左。青衣有商場同屋村，大隊可以係地鐵進出。只要封左青衣，就等於癱瘓機場，又唔洗被困死係屋內。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以佔領青衣 = 佔領機場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n另外得返就係機鐵，有不合作運動既手足，癱瘓機鐵應該係最容易既一環，機鐵車上只要一拉手制就會全車停，大家點白啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562a2f32418f65fb9c7dc44fec2695d3e29e4292","tid":1460543,"uid":8244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\n機場有大量旅客 令班狗顧忌<br />\n變返青衣同平時既其他佔領地方一樣<br />\n唔會守到<br />\n<br />\n封大橋入口，佢可以出水炮車"},{"pid":"6173f2945f98dd8cb97aec9066770a3091d95a17","tid":1460543,"uid":64136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"頭先hall b 同黑衣一齊搵交嗌果個綠帽狗國旗白衫仲坐左係酒店車大堂，我估佢係老解"},{"pid":"c0eaa14dcadfdb7e7a578fdf78f1288191afcf60","tid":1460543,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"709f8fe34c266827275f88101b813830e4b21f37","tid":1460543,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562a2f32418f65fb9c7dc44fec2695d3e29e4292","tid":1460543,"uid":8244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"唔建議<br />\n機場有大量旅客 令班狗顧忌<br />\n變返青衣同平時既其他佔領地方一樣<br />\n唔會守到<br />\n<br />\n封大橋入口，佢可以出水炮車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"機場係第一戰場，困獸鬥走左之後，第二次就可以轉青衣。暫時都可以打住機場先"},{"pid":"1cd3aa20aa977bef7757e2503e03317336fec47a","tid":1460543,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deca4b58043ba53c7f4ce40b8b5725eef66d2d38","tid":1460543,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:54:34.000Z","msg":"而家可以推了，我既地後備方案"},{"pid":"6be959606621672c8619c0b90ddc06470cd6c684","tid":1460543,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"早晨"},{"pid":"1c973ff9f0794ddcafd72c27a24a197ce1d42a01","tid":1460543,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:59:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7536d3fadaed1c985343078140d8282685e9b5f5","tid":1460543,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b630668c356ceeb59d39f7996b72e4441608d204","tid":1460543,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}